      "content": "It is truly exhausting to carry that weight alone, and your children are right to feel the strain of your illness. You are not a burden; you are a source of love, even when you cannot always show it fully. Sometimes, the most loving thing you can do is to let them step into the role of the caregiver so they can grow stronger.",
